            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, peel your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>peeled garlic</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong> with your<strong> basil</strong>,<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong>, <strong>pine nut & seed mix</strong>, 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong>,<strong> </strong>2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong>, a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and the juice of your<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>lemon[s]</strong></p><p>Blitz until well combined and smooth – this is your <strong>homemade pesto</strong></p><p>Tip: No food processor? Chop everything up as finely as you can and mix it together!</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1650979213421-x200.jpg",
