    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, transfer the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> to a clean board (discard any liquid and reserve the pan) and shred it apart, using two forks - this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1650979222363-x200.jpg",
