            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Separate the <strong>charred pepper</strong> from the <strong>cooked chorizo</strong></p><p>Spread your<strong> mayo</strong> on the<strong> warmed ciabatta base</strong> with the <strong>cooked chorizo</strong>, <strong>pesto chicken </strong>and a handful of <strong>salad</strong> and top with the <strong>warmed ciabatta lid</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>remaining salad </strong>to the side with the<strong> charred pepper </strong>and <strong>torn mozzarella </strong>on top</p><p>Drizzle over your <strong>balsamic vinegar </strong>and<strong> </strong>serve the<strong> crispy potatoes</strong> to the side and enjoy!</p>",
